The paper deals with lossy image compression using compressive autoencoders, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) research. The use of ADMM for optimization is related to information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. Finally, the focus on efficiency and optimization suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research.
